    "/analyze": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "AI分析-通用"
        ],
        "summary": "Analyze Service",
        "description": "AI原生分析端点：自然语言 → 多轮推理 → 智能组合 → 统一响应\n\n- 首次请求: 传入query，可能返回追问(needs_clarification=True)\n- 追问响应: 传入session_id + selected_option 或补充query\n- 直接指定: 传入feature_groups跳过推理\n\n可用特征组: k_patterns, lifeline, experience, ohlcv_combined, technical,\n            flow_minute, flow_daily, flow_combined",
        "operationId": "analyze_service_analyze_post",
        "requestBody": {
